info.description:
pyswarmSDK is an active light-weight MDA-style code-generator for model-driven development (MDD) of database-centric n-tier server applications. Easily customizable business-logic with Python & PostgreSQL. Applications are modeled in UML 2.0 / XMI 2.1 (XML)

(UPDATE: pyswarmSDK is a prototype built by the Aeonic project)
